description: Deirdre Morley, 43, appears in court in Dublin over the deaths of Conor, 9, Darragh, 7, and Carla, 3.
title: Woman charged with murder of her three children in Dublin
title_page: Woman charged with murder of her three children in Dublin - BBC News
maintext: The mother of three children found dead at their house in County Dublin has appeared in court charged with their murders.
